Using the famous statue of Rallos Zek Dire Charm log as a baseline here...the following AVERAGES emerge.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE CODE START--><pre> 
Class                    Dmg
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Epic Pet  Average        6071.0<br>
