<br>
So, alter &quot;tank&quot; to &quot;uncontrolled single target only root-dot&quot;<br>
<br>
THAT is what a pet is. Tanking (having played a monk far longer then a mage, and to a higher level) is more then simply providing hp's to sit there and tank damage. Tanking requires an intelligent effort. For instance, kill order, and tanking adds. I can easily hold aggro on two mobs at once. A pet can't.<br>
<br>
And, as I said before, this utility is absolutely 100% nullified if you add ANY melee of any type into the mix. This can't be said of any other class.<br>
