<br>
-Monk damage is melee damage(procs on occaision).<br>
-Magician damage is pretty well split in pet melee vs. spells.<br>
<br>
Under what conditions should the Magician damage equal the Monk damage?  <br>
<br>
Sometimes spells are more valuable and sometimes melee is more valuable, and my opinion is that spell damage is not directly compareable to melee damage due to the fact that resistance vs. AC is different on all mobs.  Also, fight length, aggro tendancies, and various AE weapons affect spell damage and melee damage differently. <p><center>
