<br>
I understand your point, but I don't think it's a good argument. <br>
<br>
Personally, I don't believe any magic should be resistable in any way, shape, or form.<br>
<br>
I personally believe all spells should land for full damage all the time, and that NEGATIVE resistances shoudl give situational bonuses. IE, instead of a fire resistant mob completely resisting char, it would get hit for full by char, and get hit for 1.1-2 times damage by our shocks.<br>
<br>
The problem is Verant put in super weapons, then made super mobs to balance them, put in mobs that were TOO powerful, so put in yet better weapons. <br>
<br>
Personally, I believe in the short term mages should out-damage monks by a great deal, and as the fight stretches monk damage should come closer to mage damage. But, I believe Magicians should always out-damage monks, and situationally out-damage rogues. I believe that in a long, drawn out fight, magicians should be right at monk damage.<br>
<br>
Edit-<br>
<br>
I know this messes up PvP. But, I think the PvP servers should be scrapped, and I know I am going to take heat for that.. but I don't care. EQ just doesn't support PvP, and a LOT of things never went in because it would too drastically alter PvP balance. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ueuripedmoped.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Euriped Moped</A> at: 2/24/02 9:01:53 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ugoladus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Goladus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Grand Poobah Goladus</span><br>  Posts: 1356<br> <font color=#333333>(2/24/02 7:35:26 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=112.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_question_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Damage: Monk &gt;= Mage + Pet &gt; Bard</span><hr size=1> I'm not really making an argument, I'm asking a question.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Under what conditions should the Magician damage equal the Monk damage?</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
